Class ClientRecord

java.lang.Object
  commandserver.ClientRecord

public class ClientRecord
extends java.lang.Object

ClientRecord - the records in the database. Includes all fields associated with a single client, except for it's uid, which the record is keyed by in the database.

Author:
W. Taff and P. Salevski
